OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A reform of Wales' political system    
OL,6, poses "a very great danger", a former  
OL,7, leader of Plaid Cymru has said.        
OL,9,FDafydd Wigley was reacting to plans to 
OL,10,Fbring in a so-called closed list PR    
OL,11,Fsystem for Cardiff Bay from 2026.      
OL,13,FThe plans were approved in principle by
OL,14,Fthe Senedd this week.                  
OL,16,FIt will be the biggest structural      
OL,17,Fchange to the electoral system since   
OL,18,Fdevolution began in 1999, and has been 
OL,19,Fdescribed by ministers as a historic   
OL,20,Fstep for the Senedd's development.     
